data.description: Huge Corner Lot with Updated Ranch Style Home! Beautifully updated 3 Bedroom, 1 Full Bath and a true 1 Car garage with Opener! A/C for those hot summer days. Newer Carpet. Newer Windows. Stucco Exterior. Oversized Kitchen with newer cabinets and tons of counter top space. Large Master Bedroom. Open Living/Dining Room Combination. Huge Laundry with room for a Pantry. Close to Preschool and Junior High School. Fully Fenced yard and ready to move in!
